# Utility Functions

The MCP Remote package includes various utility functions in [src/lib/utils.ts](mdc:src/lib/utils.ts):

## Key Constants

- `MCP_REMOTE_VERSION`: The current version of the MCP Remote package
- `AVAILABLE_PORT_START`: The starting port number for finding available ports (3000)

## OAuth and Transport Functions

- `log(str, ...rest)`: Logs a message with the process ID
- `connectToRemoteServer()`: Connects to a remote SSE server with OAuth auth
- `setupOAuthCallbackServer()`: Sets up an HTTP server for OAuth callbacks
- `findAvailablePort()`: Finds an available port on the local machine
- `getServerUrlHash()`: Generates a hash of a server URL for filenames

These utilities are used throughout the application for OAuth handling, server connections, and logging.
